Aaron Hernandez has been given prison number W106228 . 
  He will be held in maximum security at the Souza-Baranowski Correctional Center in Shirley . 
  Hernandez was transferred to the prison today after he was sentenced to life in prison for the 2013 murder of Odin Lloyd . 
  He is being held separately from other prisoners and is on suicide watch . 
  He was hooked on 'angel dust', a drug known to cause violent outbursts and paranoia . 
  Sources said he was using the drug for at least a year before Lloyd was killed . 
  He has been moved to the maximum security prison in Massachusetts . 
 